snippet.textDisplay:
Wow wow wow!  This is a Masterpiece! 

Even if you don't understand the Balochi language, you'll still love the sufi-folk feel of the first part. Then comes Ali Azmat and he hits it out of the park! His powerful yet soul-soothing vocals combined with the beautiful lyrics made this track very very different than what we have heard from this season so far. Ali Hamza and Zohaib Kazi showed their class in this track. This song has definitely raised the bar.. 

Well Done team Coke Studio!
